A vast ocean scene in Studio Ghibli style, where dozens of colorful message bottles drift on gentle turquoise waves, each bottle glowing softly with different warm hues of amber, coral, and gold. In the center, a small wooden boat with a lone figure uses a large butterfly net to gather the scattered bottles. Above, wispy clouds form interconnected spiral patterns suggesting invisible threads linking everything together. The horizon shows multiple islands in the distance, each with a distinct character - one mountainous, one forested, one with small buildings. Soft watercolor gradients blend the sky from peach to lavender as golden afternoon light catches the wave crests and bottle glass, creating scattered reflections across the water's surface.
